ved <span class=\"nowrap\">January 14,</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+angels+sang+to+Colton&amp;rft.date=2011-01-13&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flexch.com%2Farticles%2F2011%2F01%2F13%2Fnews%2Fregional%2Fdoc4d2f11b6bd5e5279630777.txt&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHeaven+Is+for+Real\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-TheScoop-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-TheScoop_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/26184891/#40888341\">\"Kathie Lee and Hoda with the Scoop\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Video(11:23))</span>. <i>The Today Show</i>. NBC.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Today+Show&amp;rft.atitle=Kathie+Lee+and+Hoda+with+the+Scoop&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ftoday.msnbc.msn.com%2Fid%2F26184891%2F%2340888341&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHeaven+Is+for+Real\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Thibault, Joanne (June 4, 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/arts-and-life/entertainment/books/near-death-experience-led-to-heavens-door-123152058.html\">\"Near-death experience led to heaven's door\"</a>. <i>Winnipeg Free Press</i>. <q>Todd is even able to report to Christian friends that Colton \"saw Mary kneeling before the throne of God and at other times standing beside Jesus.\"</q></cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2F